<L>__{interior baxter building ground floor night}
<A>__{ben pounds across the lobby. he sees johnny coming in.}
<C>__{johnny}
<D>__{christmas come early! check it out!}
<A>__{he holds up an action figure of ben: a horribly bloated body topped by a tiny pinhead. johnny pushes a button and }
<C>__{ben action figure}
<D>__{it's clobberin' time!}
<A>__{with one arm, ben shoves johnny into a wall. with his other hand, ben grabs the toy and smashes it into the wall, inches from johnny's head. the toy lodges into the plaster.}
<C>__{johnny}
<D>__{hey! that's a prototype!}
<C>__{ben}
<D>__{go back to the drawing board.}
<A>__{he strides away.}
